Installing trytontasks
======================

Prerequisites
-------------

 * Python 2.7 or later (http://www.python.org/)
 * invoke (https://pypi.python.org/pypi/invoke/)
 * See requeriments.txt

Install User DOC:

 * pip install hg+https://bitbucket.org/trytonspain/trytontasks-userdoc

Install Gal:

 * pip install hg+https://bitbucket.org/trytonspain/trytontasks-gal

Install Tests:

 * pip install hg+https://bitbucket.org/trytonspain/trytontasks-tests


Installation
------------

Once you've downloaded and unpacked the trytond_esale source release:

    invoke -l
